features: ▲ Notes: Please kindly measure your sink corner size firstly before purchasing. This triangle dish drying rack design multipurpose for sink corner. Triangular shape rack helps to make full use of your kitchen sink corner space. Efficiently dry dishes with proper drainage and ventilation. Saving counter space, easy to clean and adjustable.

▲ High Quality material: This roll up dish drying rack is made from 9pcs strong and sturdy stainless steel pipes and silicone edges with integrated design. Durable construction that will not bend or warp. Resistant to rust, non-slip and very sturdy. Easily supports heavy weights with all rod used.
▲ Foldable & Easy Storage: This dish drainer can roll up and go in a drawer to storage when not in use. Roll it up quickly and easily to put away and make your kitchen look less cluttered.

▲ Multiple Use & Heat Resistant: This sink dish drying rack not only can be used as a dish drainer for air-drying kitchenware, but also can air-drying vegetables and fruits, or as a non-slip trivet mat for hot pots or bakeware on countertop, also can be used as a sponge holder. You can wash this dish rack with hot water, even place a hot pan on the stainless steel tube of the dish rack without damaging the draining rack.

▲ Guarantee: It is our priority to give our customers the high quality product and the best service. Once you received a defective product or have any questions about the product, please feel free to contact our customer service. (Provide Refund or Exchange Service)
